_sText:
Another Simple map. This map was not based on how cool the textures are, It was based on the gameplay style and how much fun players would have on it.

Description: Basicly Objective is to Eliminate the enemy. You need to break the glass in the center then shoot your enemy. There are 2 towers with 2 AWPs on each. Those Towers are used for snipeing. There are also 4 platforms on the 4 corners of the map and those can be used for snipeing or just having a great camping time. Thats basicly it. Enjoy!!

Note 1: Sorry for only 1 screenshot. I couldn't find better spots on the map to take screens.

Note 2: Ladders are there to get on the towers and platforms.

Note 3: If you would like to use bots on this map and don't know how read my Tutorial on "How to make bots work on custom maps"

Note 4: There WILL be a Version 2 to this map where i will be adding things and making the map look better.

Hope you like the map.
